author: The Argus-Press
title: VOLLEYBALL: Laingsburg volleyball beats Saranac, improves to 6-0 in CMAC
text:
SARANAC — Erin Cooper and Sophie Strieff each had five kills to lift Laingsburg past Saranac 25-13, 25-19, 25-19 Wednesday.
